  <trk>
    <name>VIE-L2 — Wachau &amp; Waldviertel Weekend Loop — Day 2</name>
    <desc>Deploy from VIE and ride into the Wachau &amp; Waldviertel. Hit Krems an der Donau and Dürnstein Castle Viewpoint — 310m. Loop back to VIE over a packed 2–3 day weekend escape. No highways, just curves and elevation.</desc>
